com.mns.uima.utils
Class PrimitiveAFS

java.lang.Object
  com.mns.uima.utils.PrimitiveAFS

public class PrimitiveAFS
extends java.lang.Object

PrimitiveAFS holds a simplified representation of UIMA AnnotationFS

PrimitiveAFS is not a UIMA class. It is defined and used as a simple class that is easier to handle than AnnotationFS with the restriction that it can only hold features that are UIMA primitive types.
